  "title": "日不落的「喀什」",
  "summary": "6小时绿皮火车，我和x来到了喀什，地图上最西的「鸡尾巴」到达时正值饭点，于是俩人到酒店放下行李就外出觅食了，吃的抓饭。 监控看了一眼苗姐正在睡午觉，吃完饭俩人去喀什古城转了一圈，今天偷懒，不想扣字。 这会快7点了，太阳还在天空正当中，走路回酒店被晒得快中暑了，前台说这会大约晚上10点天黑，有种莫名的恍惚感。",
  "content": "<p><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2793.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2793.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1290\" height=\"919\"></a></p><p>6小时绿皮火车，我和x来到了喀什，地图上最西的「鸡尾巴」到达时正值饭点，于是俩人到酒店放下行李就外出觅食了，吃的抓饭。</p><p>监控看了一眼苗姐正在睡午觉，吃完饭俩人去喀什古城转了一圈，今天偷懒，不想扣字。</p><p>这会快7点了，太阳还在天空正当中，走路回酒店被晒得快中暑了，前台说这会大约晚上10点天黑，有种莫名的恍惚感。</p><p><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2811-scaled.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2811-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2804.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2804.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2809.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2809.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2808.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2808.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2807.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2807.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2805.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2805.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2803-scaled.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2803-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2806.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2806.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\"></a><a href=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2810-scaled.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ihaihe.cn/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMG_2810-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1919\" height=\"2560\"></a></p>",
